<p>
<lb n="1"/>namō varāharūpāya viśvarūpāya viṣṇavē <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> bhūrmmustēva saśailābdiryyaddaṁṣrāyāṁ virājatē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> yasya śrīparamēśvarasya vipulā śrīpādapadmadvayē bhaktiryyō bhuviguṁḍenāryyahridayasyānaṁdadō naṁdanaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kuppā <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>mukhavarttikīrttiniratassanmānadānākaraḥ (<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>) śrīmadguṁḍimaḍābhidhāna vibudhagrāmādhipassatyavāgdharmmatyāgadayādisadguṇadhanairākīrnnacētōgrihaḥ dhīmānkāśyapagōtravarddhanakarassāhityavidyāttadhīḥ Annākhyassukavīṁ<unclear>dra</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>tē kammakṣamāmaṁḍalē śrīmatyāptaśubhōttarāyanadinē kuppāṁbikānaṁdana<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> prādādannayanāmavānguṇanidhi<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śrīkēśavasyālayē dīpaṁ ppāpatamaḥprahāraminabhūcaṁdradyutārasthiraṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīmanmahāmaṁḍalēśvara śrī <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>dēvara kakhaṁḍavarttidīpamunakuṁ beṭṭina mēṁka 55 vīniṁ jēkoni raḍḍamunannebōyuṁḍu tana putrānupautrika mācaṁdrārkkamu nitya māneṁḍu neyi vōyaṁggalavāṁḍu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svadattaṁ paradattaṁ vā yō harēti vasu <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
